TIER 2 — Strategic depth
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Draft Combine / Deeper Scouting — measurables (40 time, bench press) that
  hint at hidden potential. Ties into the existing 25-point scouting system.

Schemes — offensive and defensive scheme selection that shapes team identity
  and influences sim output (run-heavy, pass-heavy, zone vs. man, etc.).

TIER 3 — Polish & replayability
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Team Editor — edit team name, city, colors, conference/division.

League Customization — expansion teams, relocation, custom team names.

In-Game Narrative / Play-by-Play — text play-by-play during simulation.
  Stats-only output today limits immersion significantly.

